- **User Guide**: Includes sections on introduction, product overview, sizing and fit, proper care and maintenance, break-in period, safety tips, and troubleshooting.
- **Warranty Information**: Offers a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components.
- **Contact Information**: Customer support can be reached at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com.
